HEADWORD: Standard-bred
<hw>Stand"ard-bred`</hw> <pr>(-br⟦ecr⟧d`)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Bred
in conformity to a standard. Specif., applied to a registered trotting
horse which comes up to the standard adopted by the <org>National
Association of Trotting-horse Breeders</org>.</def> <mark>[U.
S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

